{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"694ddfe8ce","title":"周居正临死前的复查记录","origin":"四川省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cbbb116cb1","index":0,"year":1964,"month":1,"day":9,"articleId":"694ddfe8ce"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c9d2879e80","type":"title","text":"周居正临死前的复查记录","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"73037b2360","type":"paragraph","text":"1964年1月9日上午10时，省高院审判员王殿理，省检察院检查员岳鸿杰提审周居正，对其进行复查。下面摘录《复查记录》内容：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"c2f9c29f01","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"f33429e73c","type":"paragraph","text":"？你对法院判决（指最高院维持原判的判决——作者注）后还有何意见？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"69cc24a247","type":"paragraph","text":"：就是我陈述报告的那些意见，就是我的实际思想。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"4ecdafd512","type":"paragraph","text":"？犯罪事实上？","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"70a12b8842","type":"paragraph","text":"：……我现在还有对事实思想上有新的贡献：1、对毛泽东的战略上重视敌人，战术上藐视敌人；2、敌人一定要灭亡；3、决定战争是人。此外，我对世界文还有贡献。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"43d284f5f8","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"776e6719a4","type":"paragraph","text":"？：你这个问题就这样了。你对犯罪事实还有何意见？","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"bfd26d469d","type":"paragraph","text":"：犯罪事实就是我原来交待的东西，是事实我就承认。不是事实就不同意。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"5a854c0983","type":"paragraph","text":"？那些不是事实？","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"608c515893","type":"paragraph","text":"：我不是“一贯反革命”。我犯罪主要三年认识错误。还有关于后果，我已叫成员目前不搞军事、经济破坏，因为，我认为目前应积蓄力量，等待时机。2、如果我将来还能工作，有些问题还能够解决，想以此来作个收场。即骑墙思想。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"ad449dfd7e","type":"paragraph","text":"？你发展这样多成员，进行了这些活动，还不算后果？","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"544e4fe3f4","type":"paragraph","text":"：这是后果……与拿起枪杆子来干有区别。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"4084769d7b","type":"paragraph","text":"？你实际已经造成了严重的后果了。你已发展这样多成员，使之反对共产党，要推翻共产党，这难道还不是后果？","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"78efd37198","type":"paragraph","text":"：我只是说未造成严重后果。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"8a97b7d5ac","type":"paragraph","text":"？你实际上已经造成严重后果了。你使这样多人起来反对共产党，要推翻共产党，这还不算严重后果？难道要杀了人才算？","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"cb13f44019","type":"paragraph","text":"：还有我手上未沾有人民的血，不是“一贯”的。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"4d9a93ccac","type":"paragraph","text":"？在你看来不算，在我们看来完全是一贯的。解放前反革命，解放后攻击党，划为右派，又进行活动，这还不是一贯是什么呢？你完全不是偶尔犯罪。","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"2ec03721da","type":"paragraph","text":"审：你这不是受蒙蔽，你有你的目的。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"41d4f120e5","type":"paragraph","text":"：如果说目的，也不是个人目的。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"f7faa33d47","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"0b1addec97","type":"paragraph","text":"？其他都是事实？","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"77bf57352d","type":"paragraph","text":"：都是事实。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"d5c429b4ee","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"9119dfc6a4","type":"paragraph","text":"？你还有什么？","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"cfe048de18","type":"paragraph","text":"：我交待的就是这些。","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"118b4b18a6","type":"paragraph","text":"？对犯罪事实就是这些？","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"5c21ba6801","type":"paragraph","text":"：就是这些，都是事实。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"2dce8ddec0","type":"paragraph","text":"？还有什么可以提出……","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"5e5b3e9c70","type":"paragraph","text":"：就是陈述报告中所提到的那些。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"760abfbd3b","type":"paragraph","text":"？你就只有你说的“三个问题”？","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"62e772ba95","type":"paragraph","text":"：还有“不是死心踏地”。因为在关押后有悔改。原来我确实是“死心踏地”的。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"204af3481f","type":"paragraph","text":"？就是这些？","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"1df2fb33ee","type":"paragraph","text":"：就是这些。","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"},{"id":"33256de66f","type":"paragraph","text":"1964年1月15日，四川省高级人民法院在永川新胜劳改茶场召开公判大会，枪杀周居正。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce"}],"page":{"id":"261a8a8fcc","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"694ddfe8ce","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}